
                              gzstream
      C++ iostream classes wrapping the zlib compression library.
===========================================================================

    See index.html for documentation and installation instructions.

    10Oct16: Mark C. Miller:
        * Modified to build in MFEM source tree and use 'mfem' namespace
        * Modified to use char *mode for constructors/open instead of int
        * Changed bufferSize from 47+256 to 8192 (8 kilobytes)
        * Other notes:
            * consider mode char options for zlib's internal buffer sizes
      
